pullRequest.bodyText:
Two goals:
(1) To support double quoted nodes in any level , e.g., root."s.g"."device.1"."sensor.1" : root -> "s.g" -> "device.1" -> "sensor.1"
(2) In antlr, a path has already been split to nodes. For example, root.sg1.d1.s1 to [root, sg1, d1, s1]. It‘s no need to generate a Path and split again in metadata, so this PR's goal is to reduce split actions in the metadata.
